article.description: — Josh Oduro scored 29 points, Bryce Hopkins had 25 points and 14 rebounds, and Providence defeated Lehigh 78-64 on Friday night.
article.headline: Providence defeats Lehigh 78-64
article.story: PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- — Josh Oduro scored 29 points, Bryce Hopkins had 25 points and 14 rebounds, and Providence defeated Lehigh 78-64 on Friday night. Oduro also had seven rebounds for the Friars (5-1). Devin Carter added 10 points. The Mountain Hawks (1-5) were led by Dominic Parolin, who recorded 18 points. Lehigh also got 16 points, eight rebounds and two blocks from Keith Higgins Jr. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
